  <data key="d1">event</data>
  <data key="d2">2000年至2022年期间是加拿大五岁以下儿童死亡率被观察和记录的时间跨度。&lt;SEP&gt;The time period spanning from year 2000 to 2022 during which Switzerland's under-5 mortality rate was observed and recorded.&lt;SEP&gt;该时期涵盖了中国五岁以下儿童死亡率从36.7下降到6.6的观察数据。&lt;SEP&gt;The 2000-2022 period represents the timeframe during which under-5 mortality rate observations were recorded for Korea, Rep.&lt;SEP&gt;The time period spanning from 2000 to 2022 during which mortality rate observations were recorded for Trinidad and Tobago.</data>
