<node id="2000">
  <data key="d0">2000</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The year 2000 marks the beginning of the mortality rate observation period for Haiti.&lt;SEP&gt;2000年是伊朗五岁以下儿童死亡率记录的起始年份，死亡率为36.3。&lt;SEP&gt;The year 2000 marks the beginning of the mortality rate observation period with a recorded rate of 10.0 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2000 recorded Sudan's under-5 mortality rate at 103.4 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;The year 2000, marking the beginning of the mortality rate observation period with a recorded rate of 30.7 per 1,000 live births.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6de7e46eb4073a6c4c1ac5780b66991a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20f235fe892bd1b54a4aaf033044667d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5115f9233064e36cc251171accb95aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8ddbc28bb924e6f0203fb6305682201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1b163544bd02b11ef1a20074c02560e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774634157</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2010">
  <data key="d0">2010</data>
  <data key="d1">data</data>
  <data key="d2">The year 2010 shows an anomalous spike in Haiti's under-5 mortality rate to 136.7 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2010 recorded Sudan's under-5 mortality rate at 74.2 per 1,000 live births.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6de7e46eb4073a6c4c1ac5780b66991a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8ddbc28bb924e6f0203fb6305682201</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
  <data key="d5">1774634129</data>
  <data key="d6"></data>
</node>
<node id="2022">
  <data key="d0">2022</data>
  <data key="d1">concept</data>
  <data key="d2">The year 2022 marks the end of the mortality rate observation period for Haiti.&lt;SEP&gt;2022年是伊朗五岁以下儿童死亡率记录的最后年份，死亡率为12.2。&lt;SEP&gt;The year 2022 marks the end of the mortality rate observation period with a recorded rate of 8.1 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2022 recorded Sudan's under-5 mortality rate at 51.8 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;The year 2022, marking the end of the mortality rate observation period with a recorded rate of 21.2 per 1,000 live births.</data>
  <data key="d3">chunk-6de7e46eb4073a6c4c1ac5780b66991a&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-20f235fe892bd1b54a4aaf033044667d&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f5115f9233064e36cc251171accb95aa&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-a8ddbc28bb924e6f0203fb6305682201&lt;SEP&gt;chunk-f1b163544bd02b11ef1a20074c02560e</data>
  <data key="d4">unknown_source</data>
