  <data key="d8">Under-5 Mortality Rate in Year 2001 was 59.1 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2001的5岁以下儿童死亡率数据为56.4例/1,000活产婴儿。&lt;SEP&gt;Year 2001 recorded an under-5 mortality rate of 94.9 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;Under-5 Mortality Rate在Year 2001的观测值为7.1。&lt;SEP&gt;The under-5 mortality rate for Chad in year 2001 was 180.2 per 1,000 live births.&lt;SEP&gt;2001年Togo的五岁以下儿童死亡率为116.0每1,000名活产婴儿。</data>
